269
00:14:34,541 --> 00:14:36,441
undo it?

270
00:14:39,170 --> 00:14:41,864
That line about "can't go back"...

271
00:14:41,864 --> 00:14:43,966
felt too cheesy.

272
00:14:43,966 --> 00:14:46,026
I currently write romance,

273
00:14:46,026 --> 00:14:48,699
but not that style.

274
00:14:52,392 --> 00:14:54,279
Good then.

275
00:14:54,279 --> 00:14:56,100
What did you say, Lawyer Xu?

276
00:15:03,070 --> 00:15:05,239
I said...

277
00:15:05,239 --> 00:15:08,179
that's good.

278
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:12,299
Just eat your congee.

279
00:15:16,625 --> 00:15:19,446
Weren't you chatting first?

280
00:15:22,631 --> 00:15:24,370
Sorry, Lawyer Xu.

281
00:15:28,136 --> 00:15:29,639
<i>Ruan Yu, look.</i>

282
00:15:29,639 --> 00:15:31,480
<i>That drunk from the other day.</i>

283
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:33,620
<i>So ridiculous.</i>

284
00:15:49,616 --> 00:15:52,757
This drunk kinda looks like...

285
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:58,659
The drunk...

286
00:16:00,039 --> 00:16:01,539
like me?

287
00:16:02,133 --> 00:16:03,240
No.

288
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:05,759
Just the build, a bit.

289
00:16:05,759 --> 00:16:07,559
You're so disciplined,

290
00:16:07,559 --> 00:16:09,159
you wouldn't drink that much.

291
00:16:09,159 --> 00:16:10,279
Even if you did,

292
00:16:10,279 --> 00:16:12,579
you wouldn't be like that.

293
00:16:21,522 --> 00:16:24,636
The video is blurry.

294
00:16:24,636 --> 00:16:27,000
A suit doesn't mean

295
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,946
you can ID him.

296
00:16:28,946 --> 00:16:30,156
One more tip.

297
00:16:30,156 --> 00:16:34,352
Tell your property team to tighten security.

298
00:16:40,639 --> 00:16:41,799
This guy

299
00:16:41,799 --> 00:16:44,086
is probably Li Shi Can's fan.

300
00:16:44,086 --> 00:16:45,840
The moves look like

301
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:48,300
Li Shi Can's dance.

302
00:16:48,300 --> 00:16:50,440
Still pretty funny.

303
00:16:58,039 --> 00:17:00,039
Let's eat.

304
00:17:00,039 --> 00:17:01,579
It'll get cold.

305
00:17:02,564 --> 00:17:03,946
Yes.

306
00:17:07,861 --> 00:17:10,720
Li Shi Can dances well.

307
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:13,532
He's a pro.

308
00:17:13,532 --> 00:17:15,426
After all, that's his job.

309
00:17:16,599 --> 00:17:19,259
Lawyer Xu, you know him too?

310
00:17:20,249 --> 00:17:22,435
Shouldn't I ask you?

311
00:17:22,435 --> 00:17:24,319
Everyone knows stars.

312
00:17:24,319 --> 00:17:25,720
But to be with one

313
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:27,546
under the same roof

314
00:17:27,546 --> 00:17:29,685
same couch...

315
00:17:29,685 --> 00:17:31,986
that's quite close, isn't it?

316
00:17:32,761 --> 00:17:34,636
You mean last time?

317
00:17:34,636 --> 00:17:36,806
I knew him before fame.

318
00:17:36,806 --> 00:17:38,182
We're college alumni.

319
00:17:38,182 --> 00:17:39,709
Not just that, huh?

320
00:17:40,982 --> 00:17:43,860
You're from the same place too.

321
00:17:45,357 --> 00:17:48,234
As how I remember it, he's from Su City, right?

322
00:17:48,234 --> 00:17:50,046
Yes.

323
00:17:50,654 --> 00:17:52,488
Met in high school?

324
00:17:52,488 --> 00:17:53,590
Not really.

325
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:54,920
He was at No.2 High.

326
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:56,380
I was...

327
00:17:59,371 --> 00:18:02,950
Which school were you at then?

328
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:07,400
I...

329
00:18:14,519 --> 00:18:16,100
I...

330
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:19,472
- Sorry, Lawyer Xu.
- It's fine.

331
00:18:19,472 --> 00:18:20,847
- I've got it.
- Sorry.

332
00:18:20,847 --> 00:18:22,160
It's okay.

333
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:23,979
Thanks.

334
00:18:31,960 --> 00:18:33,640
Lawyer Xu, let's eat first.

335
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:35,179
It'll get cold.

336
00:18:53,299 --> 00:18:57,136
Then thank that glass for its sacrifice.

337
00:18:57,136 --> 00:18:58,680
<i>You're laughing?</i>

338
00:18:58,680 --> 00:19:02,079
How is Xu Huai Song living abroad...

339
00:19:02,079 --> 00:19:06,054
How could he know that
Li Shi Can's from Su City?

340
00:19:06,054 --> 00:19:08,440
Is he that famous now?

341
00:19:08,440 --> 00:19:10,440
Not his fault.

342
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:13,361
After all, you brought him up.

343
00:19:13,361 --> 00:19:15,599
Still, I always got this feeling...

344
00:19:15,599 --> 00:19:17,240
that Xu Huai Song

345
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:19,325
has an issue with him.

346
00:19:19,325 --> 00:19:20,451
I got it.

347
00:19:20,451 --> 00:19:22,745
It's that misunderstanding.

348
00:19:22,745 --> 00:19:25,319
He even called the police.

349
00:19:25,319 --> 00:19:26,582
<i>True.</i>

350
00:19:26,582 --> 00:19:29,480
Talking to Xu Huai Song, it's all traps.

351
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:32,119
<i>One after another.</i>

352
00:19:32,119 --> 00:19:33,160
<i>From now on,</i>

353
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:35,174
I'll avoid seeing him alone.

354
00:19:35,174 --> 00:19:37,661
Or I'll slip up.

355
00:19:40,466 --> 00:19:41,972
If you ask me,

356
00:19:41,972 --> 00:19:44,920
you, instead of being on edge,

357
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:47,895
just be bold and tell the truth.

358
00:19:47,895 --> 00:19:51,160
<i>If you don't care about him,</i>

359
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:53,109
then let the past drift by

360
00:19:53,109 --> 00:19:55,880
and keep your spirit light.

361
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:57,300
Okay?

362
00:19:58,114 --> 00:20:01,273
That's not about whether I care.

363
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:05,030
I just don't want to rip off my past

364
00:20:05,030 --> 00:20:08,140
and lay it bare in the open.

365
00:20:09,079 --> 00:20:10,900
It's too embarrassing.

366
00:20:32,274 --> 00:20:33,610
Mom, Dad, I'm home.

367
00:20:33,610 --> 00:20:35,666
Our girl's back.

368
00:20:36,393 --> 00:20:38,633
Hold on, turning this off.

369
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:41,282
What's for dinner, Mom?

370
00:20:41,282 --> 00:20:42,799
Tomorrow's Winter Solstice, right?

371
00:20:42,799 --> 00:20:44,920
I'm making your dumplings.

372
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:45,960
Nice.

373
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:47,400
Then I want it with

374
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:49,039
osmanthus wine.

375
00:20:49,039 --> 00:20:51,250
Sure, I got you.

376
00:20:51,250 --> 00:20:53,212
I'll help in a second, Mom.

377
00:20:53,212 --> 00:20:54,720
Stop it, you'll just get in the way.

378
00:20:54,720 --> 00:20:55,799
You'll slow me down.

379
00:20:55,799 --> 00:20:57,039
Right?

380
00:20:57,039 --> 00:20:59,019
You're killing my vibe.

381
00:20:59,620 --> 00:21:01,319
Mom, where's Dad?

382
00:21:01,319 --> 00:21:03,137
Your dad was just here.

383
00:21:03,137 --> 00:21:05,265
- Ruan Yu's back.
- Dad.

384
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:07,920
We're in for a treat.

385
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:09,839
Thanks, Mom.

386
00:21:09,839 --> 00:21:13,119
Come on. Let's get some sun.

387
00:21:13,119 --> 00:21:14,880
Mom, I'll be outside.

388
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:16,079
You two just left me?

389
00:21:16,079 --> 00:21:17,860
No one cares?

390
00:21:23,367 --> 00:21:26,328
This weather's great.

391
00:21:26,328 --> 00:21:29,955
Still talking to Xiao Liu?

392
00:21:29,955 --> 00:21:31,834
Not again.

393
00:21:31,834 --> 00:21:33,440
I told you,

394
00:21:33,440 --> 00:21:35,459
we're not a match.

395
00:21:36,088 --> 00:21:37,640
I'm just saying,

396
00:21:37,640 --> 00:21:40,050
being a lawyer is good.

397
00:21:40,050 --> 00:21:41,677
If you get in trouble,

398
00:21:41,677 --> 00:21:44,097
he can help.

399
00:21:44,097 --> 00:21:45,160
Dad,

400
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:47,641
you want me to get in trouble?

401
00:21:47,641 --> 00:21:49,119
Kid,

402
00:21:49,119 --> 00:21:50,880
can't you tell?

403
00:21:50,880 --> 00:21:52,279
Exactly.

404
00:21:52,279 --> 00:21:53,856
Here.

405
00:21:53,856 --> 00:21:55,200
By the way,

406
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:58,776
we're going back to Su City.

407
00:21:58,776 --> 00:22:00,600
No way.

408
00:22:00,600 --> 00:22:02,446
It's been windy and rainy.

409
00:22:02,446 --> 00:22:05,480
Today's the only sunny day.

410
00:22:05,480 --> 00:22:07,313
All that travel around

411
00:22:07,313 --> 00:22:08,839
will trigger your rheumatism.

412
00:22:08,839 --> 00:22:11,872
We haven't lived there for years,
but for the Solstice,

413
00:22:11,872 --> 00:22:14,119
- we should clean it.
- Right.

414
00:22:14,119 --> 00:22:15,880
Your mom's been missing it.

415
00:22:15,880 --> 00:22:17,671
She wants to go back.

416
00:22:17,671 --> 00:22:19,039
Okay then.

417
00:22:19,039 --> 00:22:20,381
I'll go with her.

418
00:22:20,381 --> 00:22:22,323
You stay home and rest.

419
00:22:22,323 --> 00:22:23,425
Then

420
00:22:23,425 --> 00:22:25,839
I can have some alone time with Mom.

421
00:22:25,839 --> 00:22:27,400
You, honestly.

422
00:22:27,400 --> 00:22:28,599
You're all grown up,

423
00:22:28,599 --> 00:22:29,960
not with your boyfriend,

424
00:22:29,960 --> 00:22:31,480
but "alone time" with Mom?

425
00:22:31,480 --> 00:22:32,759
Exactly.

426
00:22:32,759 --> 00:22:34,395
Fine.

427
00:22:34,395 --> 00:22:35,640
Then I can only

428
00:22:35,640 --> 00:22:37,774
go along with it.

429
00:22:37,774 --> 00:22:40,027
I'd be happy to.

430
00:22:40,027 --> 00:22:42,576
Then I'll just...

431
00:22:42,576 --> 00:22:44,939
let it all be.

432
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:48,079
Alright.

433
00:22:48,079 --> 00:22:50,259
Go enjoy yourselves.

434
00:22:53,000 --> 00:22:55,340
The weather's great.

435
00:22:58,587 --> 00:23:01,559
Maybe call Xiao Liu.

436
00:23:01,559 --> 00:23:03,048
Young people

437
00:23:03,048 --> 00:23:04,717
need to meet more

438
00:23:04,717 --> 00:23:07,579
to make it work.

439
00:23:08,722 --> 00:23:11,182
Remember us back then?

440
00:23:12,333 --> 00:23:13,892
Your daughter

441
00:23:13,892 --> 00:23:16,061
if she had half your skills,

442
00:23:16,061 --> 00:23:18,693
I wouldn't worry.

443
00:23:18,693 --> 00:23:20,459
Who's she like?

444
00:23:22,839 --> 00:23:24,620
Me, of course.

445
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:41,079
Aunt Qu just texted me.

446
00:23:41,079 --> 00:23:42,599
Guess she still thinks of me.

447
00:23:42,599 --> 00:23:45,939
Even good stuff, she thinks of me.

448
00:23:48,160 --> 00:23:50,160
Unlike some people.

449
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:51,764
Once they prep for a case,

450
00:23:51,764 --> 00:23:54,960
it's been a long time since seeing Ruan Yu.

451
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:56,240
True.

452
00:23:56,240 --> 00:23:57,627
Hard to run into her.

453
00:23:57,627 --> 00:23:58,680
Not like me though.

454
00:23:58,680 --> 00:24:01,820
See? She asked me out.

455
00:24:02,900 --> 00:24:04,653
Lately,

456
00:24:04,653 --> 00:24:07,406
my neck's really stiff.

457
00:24:07,406 --> 00:24:09,908
Probably overworked.

458
00:24:12,799 --> 00:24:14,371
Must be tiring you out.

459
00:24:14,371 --> 00:24:15,799
Yeah, right there.

460
00:24:15,799 --> 00:24:17,380
A bit more pressure.

461
00:24:19,543 --> 00:24:21,003
Here, take it.

462
00:24:24,339 --> 00:24:26,079
Not bad.

463
00:24:26,079 --> 00:24:27,799
<i>Xiao Liu, last time you said</i>

464
00:24:27,799 --> 00:24:29,720
<i>you go to Su City a lot.</i>

465
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:31,470
<i>Got any plans soon?</i>

466
00:24:31,470 --> 00:24:34,493
<i>Maybe drop me and Ruan Yu at the old house?</i>

467
00:24:34,493 --> 00:24:36,279
<i>No pressure if it's a hassle.</i>

468
00:24:36,279 --> 00:24:38,480
<i>Come eat at my place sometime.</i>

469
00:24:38,480 --> 00:24:41,230
How about this,

470
00:24:41,230 --> 00:24:43,153
you handle it all.

471
00:24:44,039 --> 00:24:46,819
Reply however you want.

472
00:24:46,819 --> 00:24:48,519
Just tell her

473
00:24:48,519 --> 00:24:49,822
I'm busy.

474
00:24:49,822 --> 00:24:51,117
Or tell her

475
00:24:51,117 --> 00:24:52,640
I don't get along with her daughter.

476
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:54,219
We clash.

477
00:24:55,829 --> 00:24:57,706
For your happiness, man,

478
00:24:57,706 --> 00:24:59,666
I can take the hit.

479
00:24:59,666 --> 00:25:01,605
It's fine.

480
00:25:06,505 --> 00:25:08,759
One more thing.

481
00:25:08,759 --> 00:25:11,480
That place next door, the matchmaking agency,

482
00:25:11,480 --> 00:25:12,880
lease ends next month.

483
00:25:12,880 --> 00:25:14,640
I'm thinking

484
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:16,119
we take it over.

485
00:25:16,119 --> 00:25:17,400
Expand the office.

486
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:19,226
Make the firm bigger.

487
00:25:19,226 --> 00:25:21,671
More space, brighter.

488
00:25:22,940 --> 00:25:24,160
<i>My pleasure.</i>

489
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:25,200
<i>I've got a case tomorrow.</i>

490
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:28,720
<i>- Just leave it to me!</i>
- Not tomorrow night. I've got a date.

491
00:25:28,720 --> 00:25:30,426
Set up by that agency?

492
00:25:30,426 --> 00:25:31,799
Yes.

493
00:25:31,799 --> 00:25:34,450
You sure a place that can't even pay rent

494
00:25:34,450 --> 00:25:37,454
can secure your happiness
for the rest of your life?

495
00:25:41,333 --> 00:25:43,794
Rent needs money.

496
00:25:43,794 --> 00:25:45,533
Love doesn't.

497
00:25:48,005 --> 00:25:50,480
Daytime won't take long.

498
00:25:50,480 --> 00:25:53,419
Surely it won't ruin your date at night.

499
00:25:58,319 --> 00:26:00,880
<i>No wonder no train ticket.</i>

500
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:04,079
<i>Should've known it's this kind of ride.</i>

501
00:26:04,079 --> 00:26:05,439
Sorry, Lawyer Liu.

502
00:26:05,439 --> 00:26:06,599
Thanks for the trouble.

503
00:26:06,599 --> 00:26:07,880
No trouble.

504
00:26:07,880 --> 00:26:09,540
It's on the way.

505
00:26:11,440 --> 00:26:13,822
You really going to Su City for work?

506
00:26:13,822 --> 00:26:16,040
Yeah, doing visits.

507
00:26:16,040 --> 00:26:19,480
One client's...

508
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:20,759
old classmate

509
00:26:20,759 --> 00:26:22,359
happens to be there.

510
00:26:22,359 --> 00:26:24,400
Even old classmates get visits.

511
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:26,559
That's a lot of work.

512
00:26:26,559 --> 00:26:29,653
Tell me about it. Some clients

513
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:32,100
are really tough.

514
00:26:33,060 --> 00:26:34,119
By the way, Ruan Yu,

515
00:26:34,119 --> 00:26:36,470
I saw the location you sent.

516
00:26:36,470 --> 00:26:39,160
It's close to Xu Huai Song's grandma's.

517
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:40,641
Xu Huai Song?

518
00:26:40,641 --> 00:26:42,768
<i>My mom taught him for half a year.</i>

519
00:26:42,768 --> 00:26:44,279
<i>What if she remembers?</i>

520
00:26:44,279 --> 00:26:46,039
<i>Then we're busted.</i>

521
00:26:46,039 --> 00:26:47,816
Really? What a coincidence.

522
00:26:47,816 --> 00:26:49,599
Mom, when we get there,

523
00:26:49,599 --> 00:26:51,119
want to grab that--

524
00:26:51,119 --> 00:26:53,403
That name sounds familiar.

525
00:26:53,403 --> 00:26:55,072
Just can't recall.

526
00:26:55,072 --> 00:26:56,200
It's okay, Auntie.

527
00:26:56,200 --> 00:26:58,400
If you can't recall, just let it go.

528
00:26:58,400 --> 00:27:00,035
Not important anyway.

529
00:27:00,035 --> 00:27:01,425
Just remember me.

530
00:27:01,425 --> 00:27:03,799
Of course I do.

531
00:27:03,799 --> 00:27:04,960
You know,

532
00:27:04,960 --> 00:27:07,200
when you get older, things change.

533
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:09,670
Back in those alleys, all those kids,

534
00:27:09,670 --> 00:27:11,421
I remembered them all.

535
00:27:11,421 --> 00:27:13,759
Same with my students.

536
00:27:13,759 --> 00:27:14,799
But now,

537
00:27:14,799 --> 00:27:17,351
I forget so many.

538
00:27:17,351 --> 00:27:18,559
It's okay, Mom.

539
00:27:18,559 --> 00:27:20,720
My memory's not great either.

540
00:27:20,720 --> 00:27:22,039
See?

541
00:27:22,039 --> 00:27:24,139
Use the computer less.

542
00:27:24,139 --> 00:27:26,699
You two keep chatting.

543
00:27:34,920 --> 00:27:35,960
Listen,

544
00:27:35,960 --> 00:27:38,615
I've dropped those two off safe.

545
00:27:38,615 --> 00:27:40,119
Don't worry.

546
00:27:40,119 --> 00:27:41,519
By the way,

547
00:27:41,519 --> 00:27:44,279
got some intel for you.

548
00:27:44,279 --> 00:27:46,119
Aunt Qu said in the car

549
00:27:46,119 --> 00:27:48,599
she's meeting old coworkers today.

550
00:27:48,599 --> 00:27:51,004
Not sure if Ruan Yu'll visit school.

551
00:27:51,004 --> 00:27:53,384
Up to you.

552
00:27:58,262 --> 00:28:01,402
Liu the wingman, mission accomplished.

553
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,854
Mom, it's raining.

554
00:28:08,854 --> 00:28:10,548
Use an umbrella.

555
00:28:14,215 --> 00:28:15,475
See? Right?

556
00:28:15,475 --> 00:28:16,799
So young,

557
00:28:16,799 --> 00:28:18,880
sitting all day.

558
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,519
Move a bit, everything aches.

559
00:28:20,519 --> 00:28:23,179
What, you're old like me?

560
00:28:24,319 --> 00:28:26,622
I accept your criticism.

561
00:28:26,622 --> 00:28:29,839
I'll work out more.

562
00:28:29,839 --> 00:28:31,640
Look,

563
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:34,613
One less look each time.

564
00:28:38,180 --> 00:28:40,177
This yard, this old house...

565
00:28:40,177 --> 00:28:41,803
I really can't let go.

566
00:28:41,803 --> 00:28:43,555
Back then,

567
00:28:43,555 --> 00:28:46,683
your dad and I got married here.

568
00:28:46,683 --> 00:28:48,960
You used to play all around here.

569
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:50,103
Remember?

570
00:28:50,103 --> 00:28:52,160
I liked going there.

571
00:28:52,160 --> 00:28:54,886
Two dogs chased you. Remember?

572
00:28:57,279 --> 00:28:59,880
Speaking of that, back then,

573
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:01,939
your grandparents were still around.

574
00:29:04,661 --> 00:29:06,039
Mom,

575
00:29:06,039 --> 00:29:08,119
all our family memories

576
00:29:08,119 --> 00:29:10,200
are still here.

577
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:11,291
Come to think of it,

578
00:29:11,291 --> 00:29:14,039
we'll come back less and less.

579
00:29:14,039 --> 00:29:15,359
Not really.

580
00:29:15,359 --> 00:29:17,089
Travel's so easy now.

581
00:29:17,089 --> 00:29:19,049
I'll get a license in Hang City.

582
00:29:19,049 --> 00:29:20,842
Whenever you and Dad want back,

583
00:29:20,842 --> 00:29:22,726
I can drive you anytime.

584
00:29:22,726 --> 00:29:24,596
That'd be tiring for you.

585
00:29:24,596 --> 00:29:26,098
If you ask me,

586
00:29:26,098 --> 00:29:28,980
if my son-in-law drives, that'd be perfect.

587
00:29:28,980 --> 00:29:31,039
Mom,

588
00:29:31,039 --> 00:29:33,774
you always bring this up.

589
00:29:33,774 --> 00:29:36,149
Couldn't say it in the car.

590
00:29:36,149 --> 00:29:37,609
Lawyer Liu

591
00:29:37,609 --> 00:29:39,820
already has a new match.

592
00:29:39,820 --> 00:29:43,119
So from now on, don't trouble him.

593
00:29:43,119 --> 00:29:45,160
Really?

594
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:49,206
He seemed pretty into it. I thought...

595
00:29:49,206 --> 00:29:51,039
You'd asked him.

596
00:29:51,039 --> 00:29:53,667
Lawyer Liu is kind-hearted.

597
00:29:53,667 --> 00:29:55,544
Hard to say no.

598
00:29:55,544 --> 00:29:57,629
That's awkward.

599
00:29:57,629 --> 00:29:59,519
It's fine. So...

600
00:29:59,519 --> 00:30:01,929
if Liu's not right, there are others.

601
00:30:01,929 --> 00:30:03,160
I'll find someone.

602
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:04,160
Okay, okay.

603
00:30:04,160 --> 00:30:05,920
Take your time.

604
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:08,799
I'll grab some water.

605
00:30:08,799 --> 00:30:10,166
Go ahead.

606
00:30:10,166 --> 00:30:11,839
Let me look a bit more.

607
00:30:11,839 --> 00:30:12,936
Okay, Mom.

608
00:30:12,936 --> 00:30:14,480
<i>Boss.</i>

609
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:15,691
<i>What do you need?</i>

610
00:30:15,691 --> 00:30:16,815
<i>Soy sauce.</i>

611
00:30:16,815 --> 00:30:18,260
<i>Over there.</i>

612
00:30:25,409 --> 00:30:26,658
<i>Boss,</i>

613
00:30:26,658 --> 00:30:29,786
<i>Which one's better for cooking?</i>

614
00:30:29,786 --> 00:30:31,200
<i>At Ms. Ruan's place,</i>

615
00:30:31,200 --> 00:30:32,559
<i>your parents use this one.</i>

616
00:30:32,559 --> 00:30:34,124
<i>This one works too.</i>

617
00:30:34,124 --> 00:30:35,799
<i>What about dipping?</i>

618
00:30:35,799 --> 00:30:37,359
<i>Which tastes better?</i>

619
00:30:37,359 --> 00:30:39,160
<i>For dipping, let me see.</i>

620
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:41,440
<i>This one's good.</i>

621
00:30:41,440 --> 00:30:42,920
<i>Only for dipping?</i>

622
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,319
<i>Can it do cold dishes?</i>

623
00:30:44,319 --> 00:30:45,559
<i>Sure.</i>

624
00:30:45,559 --> 00:30:47,387
<i>Both can.</i>

625
00:30:47,387 --> 00:30:49,293
<i>Then...</i>

626
00:30:50,039 --> 00:30:52,519
<i>Then which is better value?</i>

627
00:30:52,519 --> 00:30:55,319
<i>Which won't stick when cooking?</i>

628
00:30:55,319 --> 00:30:56,960
<i>I'll pick more for you then.</i>

629
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:58,419
<i>Okay.</i>

630
00:31:02,613 --> 00:31:04,593
<i>Finally noticed me.</i>

631
00:31:08,079 --> 00:31:09,960
<i>But that look...</i>

632
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:12,540
<i>like I'm an idiot.</i>

633
00:31:22,172 --> 00:31:24,200
<i>Ten years.</i>

634
00:31:24,200 --> 00:31:26,019
<i>Everything's changed.</i>

635
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:30,620
All set?

636
00:31:31,391 --> 00:31:33,160
Yes.

637
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:35,553
Boss, I'll take this.

638
00:31:36,600 --> 00:31:38,381
Coming, Mom.

639
00:31:40,320 --> 00:31:42,720
Yeah.

640
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,257
Why's it sunny now?

641
00:31:45,257 --> 00:31:46,738
Southern weather.

642
00:31:46,738 --> 00:31:48,404
Rain on and off.

643
00:31:48,404 --> 00:31:50,835
It's noon, let's eat.

644
00:31:50,835 --> 00:31:53,160
- Sure.
- What do you want?

645
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:55,636
Up to you. I'm all good.

646
00:31:55,636 --> 00:31:56,920
Now that you mention it,

647
00:31:56,920 --> 00:32:00,000
I kinda miss the cafeteria dishes.

648
00:32:01,213 --> 00:32:03,755
<i>At noon? Cafeteria?</i>

649
00:32:03,755 --> 00:32:05,917
<i>Might run into Xu Huai Shi.</i>

650
00:32:05,917 --> 00:32:07,092
Mom,

651
00:32:07,092 --> 00:32:09,400
let's go to Old Zhou Steak House.

652
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:10,446
I'm craving it.

653
00:32:10,446 --> 00:32:12,119
Didn't you say anything's fine?

654
00:32:12,119 --> 00:32:14,440
Didn't think of it, now I really want

655
00:32:14,440 --> 00:32:15,680
the cafeteria meatballs.

656
00:32:15,680 --> 00:32:16,839
They're so good.

657
00:32:16,839 --> 00:32:18,160
And we can

658
00:32:18,160 --> 00:32:21,393
see Ms. Guo and Mr. Li, catch up.

659
00:32:21,393 --> 00:32:22,983
The more I think, the better.

660
00:32:22,983 --> 00:32:25,480
It's settled, let's go.

661
00:32:25,480 --> 00:32:26,559
You foodie.

662
00:32:26,559 --> 00:32:28,300
Eat your jelly.

663
00:32:29,157 --> 00:32:31,640
Let's hit the cafeteria.

664
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:33,000
Bring the umbrella.

665
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:34,499
Might rain again.

666
00:32:34,499 --> 00:32:36,679
- Yeah, yeah.
- Let's go.

667
00:32:45,048 --> 00:32:47,119
Youth is great.

668
00:32:47,119 --> 00:32:49,720
Used to hate uniforms.

669
00:32:49,720 --> 00:32:52,599
Now I can't even wear them.

670
00:32:52,599 --> 00:32:54,850
Then what about you, Mom?

671
00:32:54,850 --> 00:32:57,079
We're both young.

672
00:32:57,079 --> 00:32:58,685
Still young.

673
00:32:58,685 --> 00:33:00,000
How about this,

674
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:02,839
I borrow two uniforms, and we put them on,

675
00:33:02,839 --> 00:33:04,480
maybe someone'll ask,

676
00:33:04,480 --> 00:33:07,259
"Excuse me, where's the art hall?"

677
00:33:08,363 --> 00:33:09,907
What did I teach you?

678
00:33:09,907 --> 00:33:11,200
Smooth talker.

679
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:12,759
Shameless too.

680
00:33:12,759 --> 00:33:14,760
Well said.

681
00:33:15,480 --> 00:33:17,559
Auntie, three drumsticks.

682
00:33:17,559 --> 00:33:19,499
- Okay.
- I'm starving.

683
00:33:22,169 --> 00:33:23,760
- Auntie.
- Yes?

684
00:33:23,760 --> 00:33:27,137
Is Chef Cai still here?

685
00:33:27,137 --> 00:33:28,279
Which Cai?

686
00:33:28,279 --> 00:33:31,699
The one who updated the menu.

687
00:33:32,971 --> 00:33:34,759
Not a clue.

688
00:33:34,759 --> 00:33:36,480
Aunt Zhu,

689
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:37,640
it's Ms. Qu.

690
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:39,440
- Oh, hi!
- Two veggie dishes too.

691
00:33:39,440 --> 00:33:41,100
Sure.

692
00:33:41,902 --> 00:33:43,170
Since we're here,

693
00:33:43,170 --> 00:33:44,880
all those drumsticks I missed

694
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:47,200
I'll make up today.

695
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:49,699
- So good.
- Tastes great?

696
00:33:50,960 --> 00:33:53,179
Huai Shi, I'm off.

697
00:33:57,663 --> 00:33:59,623
Song,

698
00:33:59,623 --> 00:34:01,202
over here.

699
00:34:07,826 --> 00:34:09,216
What's up?

700
00:34:09,216 --> 00:34:11,134
Mom, just eat more.

701
00:34:11,134 --> 00:34:12,360
You look better with some weight.

702
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:14,721
You just said you'd eat three drumsticks.

703
00:34:14,721 --> 00:34:15,920
You were hungry.

704
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:17,055
Now you've lost your appetite.

705
00:34:17,055 --> 00:34:19,057
How can I finish three alone?

706
00:34:19,057 --> 00:34:21,760
<i>Why is Xu Huai Song here?</i>

707
00:34:21,760 --> 00:34:24,599
<i>I barely dodged his questions last time.</i>

708
00:34:24,599 --> 00:34:27,880
<i>If he sees me eating here,</i>

709
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:31,679
<i>with his old Chinese teacher,</i>

710
00:34:31,679 --> 00:34:33,989
<i>he'll know I'm from this school.</i>

711
00:34:33,989 --> 00:34:35,323
<i>Then he'll ask</i>

712
00:34:35,323 --> 00:34:37,280
<i>my class and year.</i>

713
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:40,180
<i>I might recall stuff I shouldn't.</i>

714
00:34:42,330 --> 00:34:45,466
Speaking of, when I was young,

715
00:34:46,128 --> 00:34:48,079
your dad said

716
00:34:48,079 --> 00:34:49,679
I looked like Baochai.

717
00:34:49,679 --> 00:34:51,880
I'll send the edits later.

718
00:34:51,880 --> 00:34:53,008
Okay,

719
00:34:53,008 --> 00:34:54,073
bye.

720
00:34:55,179 --> 00:34:57,400
Song, why're you back?

721
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:59,039
Felt like it.

722
00:34:59,039 --> 00:35:01,280
Tonight, let's go for

723
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:03,000
the first solstice hotpot.

724
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:04,423
Today?

725
00:35:04,423 --> 00:35:05,480
I'm busy.

726
00:35:05,480 --> 00:35:06,600
I don't buy it.

727
00:35:06,600 --> 00:35:09,360
You're free, watching me eat.

728
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:12,220
Who said I'm here for you?

729
00:35:14,240 --> 00:35:17,019
Got another sister here?

730
00:35:20,160 --> 00:35:21,624
Stop looking around.

731
00:35:21,624 --> 00:35:23,419
Focus on eating.

732
00:35:27,440 --> 00:35:29,506
It's good.

733
00:35:31,240 --> 00:35:33,179
I'm leaving.

734
00:35:34,040 --> 00:35:36,306
Song, leaving already?

735
00:35:36,306 --> 00:35:39,559
Go back and rest after.

736
00:35:39,559 --> 00:35:41,780
Wait for me.

737
00:35:44,592 --> 00:35:45,599
Ruan Yu,

738
00:35:45,599 --> 00:35:47,000
I'll go see Ms. Li.

739
00:35:47,000 --> 00:35:48,920
You look around.

740
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:55,380
It's good.

741
00:35:56,026 --> 00:35:57,440
I'll have one anyway.

742
00:35:57,440 --> 00:35:58,760
See?

743
00:35:58,760 --> 00:36:01,560
Just eat it.

744
00:36:01,560 --> 00:36:03,480
Knew you couldn't resist.

745
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:09,620
Go baseline.

746
00:36:12,119 --> 00:36:13,740
Pass it, pass!

747
00:36:14,960 --> 00:36:17,160
- Here!
- Defense!

748
00:36:20,719 --> 00:36:22,400
- Left, hurry!
- Okay.

749
00:36:22,400 --> 00:36:25,000
Dec 21, Winter Solstice.

750
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:26,480
Sunny.

751
00:36:26,480 --> 00:36:29,440
Back at Su City No.1 High.

752
00:36:29,440 --> 00:36:31,074
Watch out!

753
00:36:31,880 --> 00:36:33,280
You okay?

754
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:34,480
I'm fine.

755
00:36:34,480 --> 00:36:36,360
Didn't interrupt you writing?

756
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:38,160
No, just journaling.

757
00:36:38,160 --> 00:36:39,840
Not at all.

758
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:43,039
You still handwrite now?

759
00:36:43,039 --> 00:36:45,180
Just jotting life down.

760
00:36:46,559 --> 00:36:48,440
So artsy.

761
00:36:48,440 --> 00:36:50,880
You a writer?

762
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:53,000
I...

763
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:54,840
Kind of.

764
00:36:54,840 --> 00:36:56,579
What do you write?

765
00:36:59,080 --> 00:37:01,080
Romance.

766
00:37:05,560 --> 00:37:08,221
Then you must be good at love.

767
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:12,960
At your age,

768
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:14,559
not focusing on school,

769
00:37:14,559 --> 00:37:16,380
thinking about dating?

770
00:37:18,200 --> 00:37:20,400
Adults don't allow it

771
00:37:20,400 --> 00:37:23,720
because they worry about grades.

772
00:37:23,720 --> 00:37:25,620
My grades

773
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:28,740
can't drop any lower.

774
00:37:30,840 --> 00:37:32,119
That's actually...

775
00:37:32,119 --> 00:37:33,579
Pretty insightful.

776
00:37:34,400 --> 00:37:36,997
Either mindset or grades, you need one.

777
00:37:36,997 --> 00:37:38,880
If you've got neither,

778
00:37:38,880 --> 00:37:40,619
that's rough.

779
00:37:42,880 --> 00:37:45,459
So, the one you like, do they like you back?

780
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:52,094
Like me?

781
00:37:52,094 --> 00:37:53,800
If she doesn't hit me,

782
00:37:53,800 --> 00:37:55,760
I'm grateful.

783
00:37:55,760 --> 00:37:57,440
Then I guess

784
00:37:57,440 --> 00:38:00,880
your kind of situation is a bit like

785
00:38:00,880 --> 00:38:02,300
a crush?

786
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:09,400
Didn't expect that.

787
00:38:09,400 --> 00:38:11,939
You seem so carefree.

788
00:38:12,960 --> 00:38:14,760
Even carefree people

789
00:38:14,760 --> 00:38:18,340
in front of someone they like get cautious.

790
00:38:19,049 --> 00:38:21,989
Everyone shows it differently, that's it.

791
00:38:23,639 --> 00:38:25,220
True.

792
00:38:26,079 --> 00:38:27,639
Then tell me,

793
00:38:27,639 --> 00:38:29,979
what should I do?

794
00:38:31,895 --> 00:38:33,320
I can tell you

795
00:38:33,320 --> 00:38:34,479
how to study Chinese.

796
00:38:34,479 --> 00:38:36,400
I was pretty good at it.

797
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:37,800
So?

798
00:38:39,719 --> 00:38:41,239
You adults...

799
00:38:41,239 --> 00:38:42,780
boring.

800
00:38:43,475 --> 00:38:44,760
What's your name?

801
00:38:44,760 --> 00:38:46,400
Zhao Yi.

802
00:38:46,400 --> 00:38:49,059
Like "runaway cart-Yi." Not "iron."

803
00:39:02,050 --> 00:39:04,052
<i>When you graduate,</i>

804
00:39:04,052 --> 00:39:05,929
<i>confess to her.</i>

805
00:39:05,929 --> 00:39:07,949
<i>You have to.</i>

806
00:39:37,639 --> 00:39:38,954
Lawyer Liu,

807
00:39:38,954 --> 00:39:40,503
<i>Ruan Yu,</i>

808
00:39:40,503 --> 00:39:42,589
sorry, something came up.

809
00:39:42,589 --> 00:39:45,506
<i>This afternoon, I met two key clients.</i>

810
00:39:45,506 --> 00:39:47,199
I have to drive them to Hang City.

811
00:39:47,199 --> 00:39:48,344
So I might...

812
00:39:48,344 --> 00:39:49,512
It's fine.

813
00:39:49,512 --> 00:39:51,892
We'll take the train back.

814
00:39:51,892 --> 00:39:54,186
<i>No, don't book yet.</i>

815
00:39:54,186 --> 00:39:56,400
I still have a seat.

816
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:58,159
Enough for your mom too.

817
00:39:58,159 --> 00:40:00,639
Ride with me, it's easier.

818
00:40:00,639 --> 00:40:01,760
<i>On your way back,</i>

819
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:03,639
<i>stay safe, okay?</i>

820
00:40:03,639 --> 00:40:05,639
Okay. Thanks, Lawyer Liu.

821
00:40:05,639 --> 00:40:07,400
No problem, that's it then.

822
00:40:07,400 --> 00:40:09,574
- Bye.
<i>- Bye.</i>

823
00:40:09,574 --> 00:40:10,783
Sorry for that.

824
00:40:10,783 --> 00:40:13,280
Lawyer Liu, we shouldn't trouble you.

825
00:40:13,280 --> 00:40:14,787
We can go ourselves.

826
00:40:14,787 --> 00:40:16,750
No, it's fine.

827
00:40:16,750 --> 00:40:18,499
And my boss has already told me,

828
00:40:18,499 --> 00:40:21,296
you two must ride with me.

829
00:40:21,296 --> 00:40:22,696
Well...

830
00:40:24,239 --> 00:40:25,980
Alright.

831
00:40:32,597 --> 00:40:34,059
[Books half off. Favorites? Even more off.]

832
00:40:34,059 --> 00:40:37,479
Boss, what's the "More off"?

833
00:40:37,479 --> 00:40:39,062
Finally!

834
00:40:39,062 --> 00:40:42,649
If you were later,
I couldn't hold the good stuff.

835
00:40:42,649 --> 00:40:44,064
You've been waiting on me.

836
00:40:44,064 --> 00:40:45,276
Don't tell me

837
